  "text": "However, in a renormalizable theory of NP the operators Q eW and Q eB can only be generated at the loop-level while other operators, like the effective four-lepton couplings, can already be generated at the tree-level. In some extensions of the SM C eW and C eB may even not be generated at all [CITATION_1] .",
